mind~arrows~move around
mind~escape~go to root node
mind~return~add child node / exit edit node
mind~alt + return~backspace enter edit node
mind~tab~add siblin node
mind~delete / d~delete node and its sub-tree
mind~alt + arrows~move node with its sub-tree
mind~alt + .~toggle 'zoom in' on node
mind~space~toggle collapse
mind~ctrl + space~toggle deep collapse
mind~v~toggle outline / mindmap (outline mode is not stable)
mind~q~exit
